    <metadata>
      <schema>http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM</schema>
      <lom xsi:schemaLocation="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/lomv1.0/lomLoose.xsd" xmlns="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM">
        <general>
          <identifier>
            <catalog>oercommons.org</catalog>
            <entry>1770207219</entry>
          </identifier>
          <title>
            <string language="en">Legends of Tuskegee</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Legenden von Tuskegee</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Légendes de Tuskegee</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Legendas de Tuskegee</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Leggende di Tuskegee</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Μύθοι Tuskegee</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Leyendas de Tuskegee</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">links to three sites that look at the achievements and impact of Booker T. Washington, George Washington Carver, and the Tuskegee Airmen. In addition to general historical information, it includes snapshots of original documents and objects from the three museums and narratives that tie the three sites together.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Social Sciences</string>
          </keyword>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Links zu drei Sites, die die Ausführungen und die
Auswirkung von Booker T. Washington, George Washington von 
Tranchiermesser und von Tuskegee Fliegern betrachten. 
Zusätzlich zu den allgemeinen historischen Informationen 
schließt es Snapshots der Originalurkunden und Nachrichten von den 
drei Museen und von Darstellungen ein, die die drei zusammen Sites 
binden.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">liens à trois sites qui regardent les 
accomplissements et l'impact de Booker T. Washington, de tailleur de 
George Washington, et des aviateurs de Tuskegee. En plus de
l'information historique générale, lui inclut des instantanés des 
documents initiaux et les objets des trois musées et récits qui 
attachent les trois sites ensemble.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">ligações a três locais que olham as 
realizações e o impacto de Booker T. Washington, de carver de George
Washington, e dos aviadores de Tuskegee. Além à informação 
histórica geral, incluem instantâneos de originais originais e os 
objetos dos três museus e narrativas que amarram os três locais 
junto.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">collegamenti a tre luoghi che guardano i successi 
e l'effetto di Booker il T. Washington, del carver di George 
Washington e degli aviatori di Tuskegee. Oltre che le 
informazioni storiche generali, esso includono le fotografie 
istantanee dei documenti originali e gli oggetti dai tre musei e 
descrizioni che legano insieme i tre luoghi.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">συνδέσεις με τρεις περιοχές που εξετάζουν τα 
επιτεύγματα και τον αντίκτυπο Booker Τ. Ουάσιγκτον, του 
τροχιστή George Ουάσιγκτον, και των αεροπόρων Tuskegee. 
Εκτός από τις γενικές ιστορικές πληροφορίες, περιλαμβάνει 
τα στιγμιότυπα των αρχικών εγγράφων και αντιτίθεται από τα τρία 
μουσεία και τα αφηγήματα που συνδέουν τις τρεις περιοχές.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">conexiones a tres sitios que miran los logros y el
impacto de Booker T. Washington, del carver de George Washington, y de
los aviadores de Tuskegee. Además de la información histórica
general, él incluye fotos de documentos originales y los objetos de 
los tres museos y narrativas que atan los tres sitios juntos.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Sozialwissenschaften</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Les Sciences Sociales</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>

          </keyword>
          <keyword>

          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Ciencias Sociales</string>
          </keyword>
